        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"307953\">Ruben Van de Velde</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/Class.20extension.20and.20instance.2Freference/near/554977515\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I understand it's possible to add <code>instance [Add X] [Mul X] : TC X := TC.mk</code> or similar</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>This indeed works (and is cleaner as <code>attribute [instance] TC.mk</code>), but is usually a bad idea</p>",
